                        Patterson
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945v05</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d1086</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">1086</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-05-18T10:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-05-18T10:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-05-18T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-05-18T10:00:00-05:00" n="1086" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1086">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Control (Austria)/5–1845:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Yugoslavia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Patterson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Belgrade</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-05-18T17:00:00+02:00">May 18, 1945—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 9:15 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>95. My 88, May 16. In compliance with Deptel 91, May 16, I sent Marshal Tito a
                    note rejecting his counter proposal on Austria at 7 p.m., May 17, an hour after
                    my British colleague sent his note of rejection.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Patterson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
